		"name": "Concept Skeleton 2",
		"description": "JSON/API smoke tests for Concept Skeleton 2.\n\nBase URL: http://localhost:8088 (Docker port 8088:80).\n\nFolders:\n- **API** — `/api/*`, no CSRF, JSON forced by middleware\n- **Web GET** — test endpoints returning JSON\n- **Web POST** — run **Get CSRF token** first (stores cookie + `csrfToken` variable)\n- **Errors** — 404/500; set `APP_DEBUG=false` in `.env` for JSON error pages",
		"schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
	},
	"variable": [
		{
			"key": "baseUrl",
			"value": "http://localhost:8088"
		},
		{
